Stack: HTML/CSS/JS, Three.js, Microsoft Edge for development
The project uses ES module exports and imports
The target directory structure has a specific set of files in app/js/
Third-party libraries are stored in the lib folder and should never be edited
Microsoft Edge is the recommended browser for development and testing due to Chrome compatibility issues

